📊 Retail Sales EDA Analysis – Portfolio Project.

🎯 Problem / Goal
Identify profitability gaps across product categories and provide actionable insights, with a focus on Furniture.

🛠 Actions Taken

Cleaned and standardized dataset, including date formats.

Calculated KPIs and profit margins by category and sub-category.

Created clear, insightful visualizations for executive decision-making.

📈 Key Results

Furniture underperforming: Tables (-$17,725), Bookcases (-$3,472)

Technology and Office Supplies are the strongest performing categories

💡 Recommendations

Optimize production costs for low-performing products

Reevaluate pricing strategy for high-demand items

Adjust discount policies strategically

Rationalize product portfolio for maximum profitability

🧰 Tools Used
Excel | Python (pandas, matplotlib) | Data Visualization

✅ Outcome
Ready-to-use executive insights with actionable recommendations and visual charts to support data-driven decisions.
